SUMMARY:Migrant Justice Day: Migrant Justice Workshop
LOCATION:2100 Guy suite 205 (métro Guy)
DESCRIPTION:2026-04-10 18:30:00\n\n2100 Guy suite 205 (métro Guy)\n\nhttp
 s://www.openstreetmap.org/way/103522209\n\nWorkshop on Migrant Justice!\np
 eople move to seek safety\, opportunity\, love\, and community\; yet borde
 rs\, policing and other systemic barriers create precarity and violence fo
 r migrants\nwhen: friday april 10\, 6:30 pm\nwhere: QPIRG concordia (2100 
 rue guy\, #205)\nin this workshop\, we’ll explore the conditions that sh
 ape migration\, the struggles created by unjust systems and the powerful w
 ays migrants organize/resist\nfree and open to all! hope to see u there :3
